lot%20of%20buzz%20about%20how%20%3Cspan%3Epresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20proposed%20tariffs%20could%20negatively%20impact%20some%20of%20the%20market's%20biggest%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-hit-company-stock-profits-hardest-china-investing-manufacturing-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enames%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20of%20the%20largest%20multinational%20corporations%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20have%20heavily%20diversified%20supply%20chains%20with%20exposure%20to%20China%20and%20other%20international%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20for%20every%20company%20losing%20out%20from%20Trump's%20tariffs%2C%20there's%20another%20set%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20red%20wave%20election%20outcome.%20Tariffs%20will%20lend%20a%20helping%20hand%20to%20some%20areas%20of%20the%20US%20economy%20by%20incentivizing%20domestic%20consumption%20and%20investment%2C%20according%20to%20DWS%20Group's%20Americas%20Chief%20Investment%20Officer%20David%20Bianco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20US%20having%20shifted%20toward%20a%20service%20economy%20model%2C%20businesses%20aren't%20as%20dependent%20on%20physical%20assets%20as%20they%20were%20in%20the%20past%2C%20leaving%20them%20less%20exposed%20to%20supply%20chain%20risks%20and%20potential%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertain%20areas%20of%20the%20technology%20industry%20will%20be%20shielded%2C%20especially%20companies%20that%20don't%20manufacture%20physical%20products.%20Software%2C%20cloud%20services%2C%20and%20digital%20platforms%20have%20traditionally%20not%20been%20negatively%20impacted%20by%20protectionist%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it%20be%20software%20as%20a%20service%2C%20internet%2C%20social%20media%2C%20digital%20technology%2C%20or%20communications%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20not%20too%20worried%20about%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Bianco%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20big%20winner%20from%20tariffs%20and%20Trump%20policies%20in%20general%20is%20the%20financial%20sector.%20Banks%20are%20another%20great%20example%20of%20businesses%20that%20don't%20depend%20on%20imports.%20Regional%20banks%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20very%20little%20exposure%20to%20non-US%20revenues.%20According%20to%20Clayton%20Gardner%2C%20co-CEO%20of%20wealth%20management%20firm%20Titan%2C%20banks%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20receive%20an%20additional%20boost%20from%20deregulation%20under%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20Gardner%20believes%20low-margin%2C%20cyclical%20businesses%20with%20little%20international%20exposure%20will%20be%20the%20biggest%20winners%20from%20Trump's%20policies.%20These%20businesses%20will%20experience%20minimal%20impact%20from%20tariffs%20while%20also%20benefitting%20from%20lower%20corporate%20taxes%2C%20which%20Gardner%20expects%20to%20go%20down%20under%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20might%20interact%20with%20some%20of%20these%20companies%2C%20which%20Gardner%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bgood%20old-fashioned%20American%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20basis.%20They%20include%20grocery%20stores%2C%20dollar%20stores%2C%20home%20builders%2C%20and%20small%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20razor-thin%20margins%20as%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Gardner%20said.%20As%20margins%20start%20to%20improve%20due%20to%20lower%20corporate%20taxes%2C%20deregulation%2C%20and%20increased%20domestic%20demand%2C%20these%20companies%20will%20see%20an%20outsize%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20smaller%20manufacturing%20companies%20might%20come%20out%20as%20the%20biggest%20winners%20of%20the%20Trump%20presidency%2C%20according%20to%20Samuel%20Rines%2C%20macro%20strategist%20at%20WisdomTree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERines%20anticipates%20that%20the%20tariffs%20will%20make%20a%20compelling%20case%20for%20companies%20to%20move%20their%20operation%20to%20America.%20He%20points%20to%20Kentucky%20and%20Tennessee%2C%20two%20automobile%20manufacturing%20hotspo