%20during%20elections%2C%20AI%20has%20immense%20power%20to%20shape%20human%20lives.%20The%20pressing%20question%20is%3A%20will%20we%20act%20on%20the%20warning%20signs%2C%20or%20are%20we%20heading%20towards%20another%20preventable%20crisis%20where%20ordinary%20people%20bear%20the%20cost%20of%20corporate%20choices%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20A%20Corporate%20Buzzword%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CResponsible%20AI%E2%80%9D%20has%20become%20the%20tech%20industry's%20latest%20catchphrase.%20Much%20like%20%E2%80%9Ceco-friendly%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Ccorporate%20social%20responsibility%E2%80%9D%2C%20it's%20a%20term%20companies%20use%20to%20assure%20us%20they're%20committed%20to%20ethical%20practices.%20But%20what%20does%20%E2%80%9CResponsible%20AI%E2%80%9D%20really%20mean%2C%20and%20does%20it%20amount%20to%20genuine%20accountability%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20cases%2C%20%E2%80%9CResponsible%20AI%E2%80%9D%20ends%20up%20being%20more%20of%20a%20marketing%20slogan%20than%20a%20commitment%20to%20action.%20Companies%20publish%20ethical%20guidelines%2C%20but%20without%20mechanisms%20to%20enforce%20them%2C%20these%20guidelines%20often%20remain%20just%20words%20on%20paper.%20Similar%20to%20how%20%E2%80%9Cgreenwashing%E2%80%9D%20can%20mask%20the%20true%20environmental%20impact%20of%20corporate%20activities%2C%20%E2%80%9CResponsible%20AI%E2%80%9D%20allows%20companies%20to%20self-regulate%20while%20projecting%20an%20image%20of%20ethical%20responsibility.%20This%20reliance%20on%20voluntary%20standards%20sidesteps%20real%20accountability%20and%20leaves%20the%20public%20vulnerable%20to%20unchecked%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20Views%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20debate%20over%20AI%20safety%2C%20two%20main%20viewpoints%20have%20emerged.%20The%20first%20sees%20AI%20as%20just%20another%20technology%20that%20should%20evolve%20naturally%2C%20with%20minimal%20regulation%20to%20encourage%20innovation.%20Advocates%20of%20this%20view%20believe%20that%20companies%2C%20guided%20by%20%E2%80%9CResponsible%20AI%E2%80%9D%20principles%2C%20will%20self-regulate%20effectively.%20They%20focus%20on%20addressing%20immediate%20issues%20like%20bias%20and%20data%20privacy%20but%20resist%20strict%20regulatory%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20viewpoint%20warns%20that%20AI%20could%20eventually%20pose%20a%20fundamental%20threat%20to%20humanity.%20As%20AI%20systems%20become%20more%20advanced%2C%20they%20could%20operate%20autonomously%20and%20make%20decisions%20beyond%20our%20control.%20This%20group%20urges%20for%20strict%2C%20preemptive%20regulations%2C%20akin%20to%20those%20governing%20nuclear%20energy%20or%20biological%20weapons.%20They%20caution%20that%20without%20proper%20safeguards%2C%20AI%20might%20act%20on%20unintended%20objectives%20or%20evolve%20in%20ways%20that%20could%20harm%20us%20on%20a%20massive%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20deeply%20interested%20in%20AI%20but%20cautious%20about%20its%20unchecked%20growth%2C%20I%20see%20merit%20in%20both%20perspectives.%20AI%20holds%20incredible%20promise%20for%20advancing%20society%2C%20but%20history%20shows%20that%20leaving%20corporations%20to%20regulate%20themselves%20often%20leads%20to%20disaster.%20We%20need%20a%20balanced%20approach%20that%20ensures%20AI%20develops%20safely%2C%20guided%20by%20thoughtful%20oversight%20rather%20than%20reactive%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20AI%20Risks%20Escalate%20Quickly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20isn't%20like%20traditional%20technologies%20because%20it%20can%20learn%20and%20make%20decisions%20on%20its%20own.%20Unlike%20a%20machine%20that%20only%20does%20what%20it's%20programmed%20to%20do%2C%20AI%20systems%20can%20adapt%20and%20change%20their%20behaviour%20based%20on%20new%20data.%20This%20ability%20to%20self-learn%20means%20that%20small%20issues%20can%20quickly%20become%20big%20problems%20if%20not%20properly%20managed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20proper%20oversight%2C%20AI%20can%20amplify%20existing%20biases%2C%20ignore%20ethical%20considerations%2C%20or%20prioritise%20efficiency%20over%20safety.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20an%20AI%20system%20learns%20from%20biased%20data%2C%20it%20might%20make%20unfair%20decisions%20that%20discriminate%20against%20certain%20groups%20of%20people.%20In%20sensitive%20areas%20like%20finance%2C%20healthcare%2C%20or%20law%20enforcement%2C%20such%20outcomes%20can%20have%20serious%2C%20far-reaching%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Story%20Of%20Williams%2C%20Oliver%20And%20Parks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20risks%20aren't%20just%20theoretical%E2%80%94they're%20happening%20right%20now.%20Consider%20the%20cases%20of%20Robert%20Williams%2C%20Michael%20Oliver%2C%20and%20Nijeer%20Parks%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20All%20three%20men%20were%20wrongfully%20arrested%20due%20to%20misidentification%20by%20facial%20recognition%20technology%2C%20causing%20significant%20emotional%20and%20economic%20distress.%20Nijeer%20Parks%20spent%2010%20days%20in%20jail%2C%20while%20Michael%20Oliver%20lost%20his%20job.%20Despite%20the%20charges%20eventually%20being%20dropped%2C%20the%20arrests%20had%20lasting%20impacts%20on%20their%20relationships%20and%20personal%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20incidents%20highlight%20how%20flawed%20AI%20systems%20can%20have%20devastating%20personal%20impacts.%20Facial%20recognition%20technology%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20be%20less%20accurate%20in%20identifying%20people%20with%20darker%20skin%20tones%2C%20leading%20to%20wrongful%20arrests%20and%20unjust%20targeting%20of%20minorities.%20When%20technology%20intended%20to%20enhance%20security%20ends%20up%20violating%20individual%20rights%2C%20it%20underscores%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20financial%20sector%2C%20AI%20algorithms%20used%20to%20determine%20creditworthiness%20have%20been%20found%20to%20replicate%20racial%20and%20gender%20biases.%20This%20means%20qualified%20applicants%20might%20be%20denied%20loans%20simply%20because%20the%20AI%20has%20learned%20to%20associate%20certain%20demographic%20factors%20with%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20Whisper%2C%20a%20tool%20designed%20to%20transcribe%20speech%2C%20sometimes%20%E2%80%9Challucinates%E2%80%9D%20by%20inventing%20words%20or%20phrases%20that%20were%20never%20spoken.%20In%20critical%20fields%20like%20medicine%20or%20law%2C%20such%20errors%20could%20lead%20to%20serious%20misunderstandings%20or%20wrongful%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20examples%20underscore%20a%20vital%20question%3A%20who%20is%20responsible%20when%20an%20AI%20system%20causes%20harm%3F%20When%20algorithms%20make%20decisions%20that%20affect%20real%20lives%2C%20accountability%20cannot%20be%20an%20afterthought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECitizens%20First%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20AI%20is%20increasingly%20being%20adopted%20across%20various%20sectors%2C%20from%20agriculture%20to%20AI-driven%20education%20platforms.%20While%20these%20technologies%20offer%20significant%20benefits%2C%20they%20also%20raise%20concerns%20about%20privacy%2C%20data%20security%2C%20and%20potential%20misuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20predictive%20policing%20has%20sparked%20debates%20about%20surveillance%20and%20civil%20liberties.%20In%20education%2C%20AI%20tools%20aimed%20at%20personalising%20learning%20have%20faced%20criticism%20for%20reinforcing%20existing%20inequalities%20due%20to%20uneven%20access%20to%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20local%20examples%20illustrate%20that%20AI's%20impact%20is%20not%20just%20a%20global%20issue%20but%20one%20that%20affects%20communities%20and%20individuals%20across%20India.%20Addressing%20these%20challenges%20requires%20not%20only%20technological%20solutions%20but%20also%20thoughtful%20policies%20that%20protect%20citizens'%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20Beyond%20Buzzwords%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20%E2%80%9CResponsible%20AI%E2%80%9D%20is%20to%20be%20more%20than%20a%20buzzword%2C%20we%20need%20concrete%20actions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilt-in%20Safety%20Mechanisms%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0AI%20systems%20should%20be%20designed%20with%20safety%20features%20that%20prevent%20unethical%20or%20autonomous%20actions%20without%20human%20oversight.%20Just%20as%20cars%20come%20with%20brakes%20and%20seat%20belts%2C%20AI%20should%20have%20built-in%20safeguards.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegular%20Monitoring%20and%20Audits%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Continuous%20monitoring%20is%20essential%2C%20especially%20for%20AI%20used%20in%20high-stakes%20situations.%20Independent%20audits%20can%20identify%20issues%20before%20they%20escalate%2C%20assessing%20both%20technical%20performance%20and%20ethical%20compliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETiered%20Regulation%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Not%20all%20AI%20applications%20carry%20the%20same%20level%20of%20risk.%20We%20should%20have%20a%20tiered%20regulatory%20framework%20where%20AI%20used%20in%20critical%20sectors%20like%20healthcare%20or%20finance%20undergoes%20rigorous%20testing%20and%20certification.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependent%20Oversight%20and%20Enforcement%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Relying%20on%20companies%20to%20police%20themselves%20is%20insufficient.%20Independent%20regulatory%20bodies%20with%20the%20authority%20to%20enforce%20standards%20are%20crucial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransparency%20and%20Explainability%20Requirements%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20with%20AI%20is%20its%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20box%E2%80%9D%20nature%2C%20where%20even%20experts%20can't%20always%20explain%20how%20it%20reaches%20certain%20decisions.%20Demanding%20transparency%20and%20explainability%20ensures%20that%20AI%20systems%20can%20be%20scrutinised%20and%20held%20accountable.%20If%20an%20AI%20system%20denies%20someone%20a%20loan%20or%20recommends%20a%20medical%20treatment%2C%20we%20should%20be%20able%20to%20understand%20why.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHuman%20Rights%20In%20The%20Age%20of%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAI%20safety%20isn't%20just%20about%20preventing%20technical%20errors%3B%20it's%20about%20safeguarding%20fundamental%20human%20rights%20like%20privacy%2C%20fairness%2C%20and%20equality.%20Algorithms%20can%20entrench%20discrimination%2C%20often%20without%20anyone%20realising%20it%20until%20harm%20has%20been%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20an%20AI%20hiring%20tool%20is%20biased%20against%20women%2C%20it%20can%20systematically%20exclude%20qualified%20candidates%2C%20perpetuating%20gender%20inequality%20in%20the%20workplace.%20Protecting%20human%20rights%20means%20designing%20AI%20systems%20that%20respect%20these%20rights%20from%20the%20ground%20up%E2%80%94a%20concept%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9Cethical%20by%20design%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20white%20paper%20emphasises%20aligning%20AI%20with%20values%20like%20justice%20and%20privacy%2C%20but%20these%20principles%20need%20to%20be%20enforced%2C%20not%20just%20espoused.%20It's%20not%20enough%20to%20aim%20for%20ethical%20AI%3B%20we%20must%20ensure%20that%20ethical%20considerations%20are%20embedded%20in%20every%20stage%20of%20AI%20development%20and%20deployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccountability%20Is%20Shared%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsuring%20AI%20accountability%20isn't%20just%20the%20job%20of%20governments%20or%20corporations%3B%20it's%20a%20collective%20effort.%20International%20cooperation%20can%20help%20establish%20common%20standards%2C%20much%20like%20global%20agreements%20on%20environmental%20protection%20or%20nuclear%20non-proliferation.%20Moreover%2C%20public%20awareness%20and%20engagement%20are%20crucial.%20By%20staying%20informed%20and%20voicing%20concerns%2C%20individuals%20can%20influence%20policies%20and%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragedy%20of%20Bhopal%20teaches%20us%20that%20neglecting%20accountability%20can%20lead%20to%20catastrophic%20outcomes.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20lack%20of%20technology%20that%20caused%20the%20disaster%3B%20it%20was%20a%20failure%20to%20prioritise%20human%20lives%20over%20corporate%20interests.%20With%20AI%2C%20we're%20at%20a%20similar%20crossroads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BJibu%20Elias%20is%20an%20AI%20ethicist%2C%20activist%2C%20researcher%2C%20and%20currently%20the%20Country%20Lead%20(India)%20for%20the%20Responsible%20Computing%20Challenge%20at%20Mozilla%20Foundation%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20authors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731663720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Flv3qf9do_ai_625x300_15_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-eyewash-that-is-responsible-ai-techs-latest-buzzword-7025349%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Who%20is%20responsible%20when%20an%20AI%20system%20causes%20harm%3F%20When%20algorithms%20make%20decisions%20that%20affect%20real%20lives%2C%20accountability%20cannot%20be%20an%20afterthought.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-eyewash-that-is-responsible-ai-techs-latest-buzzword-7025349%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TVS'%20Srinivasan%2C%20Star%20Health%20founder%20launch%20health%20insurance%20product%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731663712000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftvs-s-chairman-star-health-founder-join-hands-for-galaxy-health-insurance-124111500920_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Plan%20allows%20customers%20to%20make%20multiple%20claims%20within%20same%20policy%20year%22%2C%22author%