%20smaller%20than%20proposed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-higher-inflation-fed-interest-rates-taxes-mortgage-rates-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20big%20plans%20for%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20implemented%2C%20Americans%20could%20see%20prices%20rise%20across%20several%20product%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20that%20produce%20apparel%20and%20auto%20parts%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-raising-prices-trump-tariffs-inflation-goods-getting-more-expensive-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20started%20preparing%20to%20raise%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20Trump%20enacts%20his%20plans%2C%20and%20some%20trade%20experts%20predicted%20that%20a%20range%20of%20industries%2C%20including%20electronics%20and%20appliances%2C%20would%20see%20higher%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMary%20Lovely%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20nonpartisan%20Peterson%20Institute%20for%20International%20Economics%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Trump%20could%20implement%20his%20proposed%20tariff%20on%20China%20imports%20quickly%20%E2%80%94%20within%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025%20%E2%80%94%20using%20an%20authority%20in%20the%20Trade%20Act%2C%20but%20she%20said%20it's%20a%20possibility%20that%20the%20president-elect%20will%20not%20follow%20through%20on%20the%2060%25%20tariff%20he%20proposed%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail.%20He%20also%20proposed%20a%2010%25%20to%2020%25%20tariff%20on%20goods%20imported%20from%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20taxed%20at%2060%25%20right%20now%2C%20so%20every%20sector%20is%20vulnerable%20to%20seeing%20higher%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Lovely%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20would%20expect%20a%20lower%20tariff%2C%20like%2020%25%20or%2025%25.%20There's%20also%20the%20question%20of%20how%20much%20of%20the%20tariff%20burden%20will%20fall%20on%20consumers%2C%20Lovely%20said%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20depends%20on%20the%20mechanisms%20Trump%20uses%20to%20implement%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcost-expensive-goods-price-impact-presidential-election-scenarios-trump-harris-2024-10%23imported-goods%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20tariff%20proposals%20would%20not%20impact%20consumer%20prices%20and%20would%20serve%20as%20a%20tax%20on%20other%20countries%20and%20boost%20American%20manufacturing.%20The%20impacts%20of%20his%20previous%20tariffs%20were%20mixed.%20In%202018%2C%20for%20example%2C%20tariffs%20on%20washing%C2%A0machines%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2Fbusiness%2Ftrump-tariffs-washing-machines.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaused%3C%2Fa%3E%20prices%20to%20rise%20on%20laundry%20items.%20The%20smaller%2030%25%20to%2050%25%20tariffs%20on%20imports%20from%20China%20that%20Trump%20implemented%20in%20his%20first%20term%20were%20not%20found%20to%20be%20inflationary%2C%20and%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20kept%20most%20of%20them%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsumers%20are%20going%20to%20be%20at%20a%20burden%2C%20but%20it%20may%20take%20some%20time%20for%20them%20to%20feel%20it%2C%20like%20a%20slow%20drip%2C%26quot%3B%20Lovely%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EJonathan%20Gold%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20supply%20chain%20and%20customs%20policy%20at%20the%20National%20Retail%20Federation%2C%20said%20it's%20reasonable%20for%20both%20companies%20and%20consumers%20to%20prepare%20for%20higher%20prices.%20He%20told%20BI%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecompanies%20are%20already%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20it's%20a%20finished%20good%20or%20an%20input%20to%20production%2C%20anything%20that%20gets%20brought%20into%20the%20country%20from%20somewhere%20else%20is%20going%20to%20get%20hit%20with%20that%20tax%2C%26quot%3B%20Gold%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20tariffs'%20impacts%20on%20inflation%2C%20Trump's%20spokesperson%20Karoline%20Leavitt%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20his%20first%20term%2C%20President%20Trump%20instituted%20tariffs%20against%20China%20that%20created%20jobs%2C%20spurred%20investment%2C%20and%20resulted%20in%20no%20inflation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20analyses%20from%20economists%20and%20trade%20experts%2C%20here%20are%20the%20goods%20that%20could%20become%20more%20expensive%20for%20Americans%20under%20Trump's%20tariff%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bd7d9e5-1349-490e-afe7-bfcfe6c706de%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Apparel%20and%20shoes%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EApparel%20and%20shoes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Trump's%20proposals%20in%20place%2C%20the%20National%20Retail%20Federation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nrf.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-11%2FEstimated_Impacts_of_Proposed_Tariffs_on_Imports_11.24_0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20prices%20for%20apparel%20would%20increase%20by%2012.5%25%2C%20prices%20for%20footwear%20would%20increase%20by%2018.1%25%2C%20and%20travel%20goods%20%E2%80%94%20which%20include%20backpacks%20and%20wallets%20%E2%80%94%20would%20increase%20by%2013%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetailers%20that%20source%20more%20than%2020%25%20of%20their%20goods%20from%20China%2C%20including%20Crocs%20and%20American%20Eagle%2C%20are%20at%20higher%20risk%20from%20Trump's%20tariff%20proposals%2C%20a%20Bank%20of%20America%20research%20note%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F11%2F06%2Ftrump-proposed-tariffs-consumer-prices.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20two%20companies%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20on%20whether%20they%20are%20adjusting%20their%20business%20plans%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20retailers%20have%20already%20announced%20preparations%20to%20increase%20prices%20should%20Trump's%20tariff%20plans%20go%20into%20effect.%20Columbia%20Sportswear%20CEO%20Tim%20Boyle%20said%20during%20an%20October%20earnings%20call%20that%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20concerned%20about%20the%20imposition%20of%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%20He%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2024%2F10%2F30%2Fcompanies-tariffs-trump-prices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20Washington%20Post%20that%20the%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bset%20to%20raise%20prices%26quot%3B%20in%20response%20to%20Trump's%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22901a0f6a-c8c4-4040-adc4-f59680460559%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Electronics%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectronics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20October%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop.cta.tech%2Fproducts%2Fhow-the-proposed-trump-tariffs-increase-prices-for-consumer-technology-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Consumer%20Technology%20Association%20estimated%20that%20the%20proposed%20tariffs%20would%20increase%20laptop%20and%20tablet%20costs%20by%2045%25%2C%20smartphone%20costs%20by%2025.8%25%2C%20video%20game%20consoles%20by%2039%25%2C%20and%20televisions%20by%209%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20a%20major%20supplier%20of%20electronic%20products%2C%20so%20everyday%20products%20that%20Americans%20use%20%E2%80%94%20like%20smartphones%20and%20laptops%20%E2%80%94%20would%20likely%20see%20price%20increases.%20The%20CTA%20report%20said%20that%20in%202023%2C%20China%20accounted%20for%2087%25%20of%20US%20video%20game%20console%20imports%2C%2078%25%20of%20smartphone%20imports%2C%20and%2079%25%20of%20laptop%20and%20tablet%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20companies%20could%20try%20to%20shift%20their%20production%20out%20of%20China%2C%20Gold%20said%20it's%20not%20an%20easy%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20change%20a%20supply%20chain%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20Gold%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20months%2C%20if%20not%20years%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20find%20a%20new%20vendor%20that%20you're%20comfortable%20with%20that%20can%20meet%20all%20of%20your%20different%20requirements%2C%20has%20the%20capacity%2C%20the%20skilled%20workforce%2C%20the%20infrastructure%20works%20within%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224af3509a-5a51-43d4-a381-392f563c0881%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cars%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECars%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20car%20companies%20import%20auto%20parts%20from%20China%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Europe%2C%20and%20some%20executives%20have%20already%20warned%20that%20the%20industry%20would%20likely%20face%20higher%20prices%20under%20Trump's%20tariffs.%20Philip%20Daniele%2C%20CEO%20of%20auto-parts%20company%20AutoZone%2C%20said%20during%20a%20September%20earnings%20call%20that%20if%20Trump%20carries%20out%20his%20tariff%20plans%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20pass%20those%20tariff%20costs%20back%20to%20the%20consumer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20generally%20raise%20prices%20ahead%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Daniele%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20prices%20would%20settle%20over%20time.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20that's%20historically%20what%20we've%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShinji%20Aoyama%2C%20Honda's%20executive%20vice%20president%2C%20said%20on%20a%20November%20earnings%20call%20that%20Trump's%20proposals%20will%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20impact%26quot%3B%20not%20just%20on%20Honda%20but%20on%20other%20car%20companies%20like%20General%20Motors%20and%20Ford.%20Still%2C%20he%20said%20he%20thinks%20it%20would%20take%20some%20time%20for%20the%20tariffs%20to%20be%20imposed%2C%20and%20at%20that%20point%2C%20Honda%20might%20consider%20moving%20production%20to%20a%20country%20that%20is%20not%20subjected%20to%20US%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovely%20said%20that%20auto%20parts%20are%20an%20area%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20production%20is%20coming%20from%20China%2C%20so%20it's%20%26quot%3Bvery%20reasonable%26quot%3B%20to%20prepare%20for%20price%20increases.%20But%20shifting%20production%20would%20present%20difficulties%20because%20if%20Trump%20implements%20his%2010%25%20to%2020%25%20universal%20tariff%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20don't%20really%20know%20if%20there's%20any%20safe%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228651f485-c0c8-4b71-a554-448306a5b630%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Furniture%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFurniture%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Retail%20Federation%20report%20estimated%20that%20a%2010%25%20universal%20tariff%20and%20a%2060%25%20tariff%20on%20imports%20from%20China%20would%20increase%20furniture%20costs%20by%206.4%25.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20report%20said%20a%20%24200%20crib%20could%20end%20up%20costing%20%24213%20after%20tariffs%2C%20and%20a%20%242%2C000%20mattress%20and%20box%20spring%20could%20rise%20to%20%242%2C128.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NRF%20added%20in%20its%20report%20that%20the%20higher%20costs%20would%20hit%20low-income%20households%20the%20hardest%3A%20%26quot%3BThey%20spend%20twice%20as%20much%20of%20their%20after-tax%20income%20on%20furniture%20as%20high-income%20households.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Henrik%20Elm%2C%20the%20CFO%20for%20Inter%20Ikea%20%E2%80%94%20the%20group%20that%20connects%20Ikea%20stores%20with%20suppliers%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fretail-consumer%2Fikea-ready-potential-tariffs-under-trump-cfo-says-2024-11-08%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Reuters%20that%20the%20company%20is%20preparing%20for%20higher%20tariffs%20under%20Trump%2C%20saying%20that%20Ikea%20has%20worked%20to%20make%20its%20supply%20chain%20more%20responsive%20to%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20are%20better%20equipped%20than%20we%20have%20been%20ever%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Elm%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bof%20course%20we%20are%20not%20immune%20to%20changes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b90402b-7b3d-4fb9-b4c4-8ce9e4ee75d4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Appliances%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAppliances%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENPR%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2019%2F04%2F09%2F711001915%2Ftariffs-complex-ripple-effects-hit-appliance-shoppers-and-makers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%20that%20Americans%20were%20seeing%20higher%20prices%20on%20appliances%20like%20washing%20machines%20after%20Trump%20implemented%20a%2020%25%20tariff%20on%20the%20product.%20The%20NRF%20report%20said%20it%20expects%20appliance%20pieces%20to%20rise%20again%20under%20Trump's%20higher%20tariff%20proposals%20with%20a%2019.4%25%20price%20increase%20on%20items%20including%20stoves%2C%20fridges%2C%20dishwashers%2C%20and%20blenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20analysis%2C%20the%20price%20of%20a%20basic%20fridge%20would%20rise%20from%20about%20%24650%20to%20%24776.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20said%20it's%20unlikely%20Trump's%20tariffs%20would%20go%20into%20effect%20on%20day%20one%20or%20day%20two%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bit's%20tough%20to%20say%20right%20now%20at%20what%20point%20consumers%20would%20feel%20the%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20also%20depend%20upon%20the%20individual%20companies%20and%20what%20their%20tariff%20mitigation%20plans%20are%20and%20how%20much%20they%20can%20try%20and%20lessen%20the%20impact%20on%20the%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20Gold%20said.%20%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20larger%20companies%20might%20have%20little%20more%20ability%20to%20do%20that%20than%20small%2C%20medium-sized%20folks%20who%20really%20can't%20absorb%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20tariff%20and%20would%20immediately%20have%20to%20pass%20on%20those%20costs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e555aa7a-b2a3-4f94-b3aa-dae3f12d768a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Groceries%5C%22%3EGroceries%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Groceries%5C%22%3ETrump%20vowed%20to%20lower%20grocery%20prices%20for%20Americans%20%E2%80%94%20during%20a%20town%20hall%20in%20September%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20lower%20grocery%20prices%20by%20restricting%20food%20imports%20to%20promote%20production%20in%20the%20US.%20However%2C%20his%20tariff%20plans%20could%20increase%20grocery%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Groceries%5C%22%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thirdway.org%2Freport%2Fwhat-trumps-tariffs-mean-for-your-trip-to-the-store%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20centrist%20think%20tank%20ThirdWay%20said%20that%20Trump's%20tariff%20proposals%20analyzed%20eight%20common%20purchases%20that%20the%20US%20either%20heavily%20imports%20or%20is%20unable%20to%20produce%20domestically.%20Using%20data%20from%20the%20International%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20the%20report%20estimated%20that%20coffee%20costs%20would%20rise%20by%20%240.23%2C%20frozen%20beef%20prices%20would%20rise%20by%20%241.09%2C%20and%20olive%20oil%20prices%20would%20rise%20by%20%240.31.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Groceries%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Rogers%2C%20the%20Republican%20National%20Committee%20spokesperson%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3BTrump%20will%20once%20again%20cut%20taxes%20and%20unleash%20American%20energy%20to%20lower%20prices%20on%20groceries%20and%20other%20goods%20when%20we%20send%20him%20back%20to%20the%20White%20House.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariffs-will-impact-prices-technology-clothes-appliances-furniture-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731661441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673374cb5ec9bfa3d63d81ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariffs-will-impact-prices-technology-clothes-appl