ger%20Rick%20Ratzel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20makes%20graphics%20processing%20units%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpu-rich-vs-gpu-poor-tech-companies-in-each-group-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPUs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20computer%20chips%20that%20handle%20many%20tasks%20simultaneously.%20Hence%20the%20term%20parallel%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chips%20that%20most%20people%20know%20are%20central%20processing%20units%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-a-cpu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECPUs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You'll%20find%20them%20in%20your%20laptop%20handling%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20tasks.%20While%20quick%20and%20efficient%2C%20they%20generally%20handle%20these%20tasks%20one%20at%20a%20time%20in%20a%20prescribed%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGPUs%20are%20perfect%20for%20the%20massive%20data-crunching%20that's%20needed%20to%20build%20and%20run%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-players-startups-ai-inference-driving-prices-down-cheap-workload-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20models%20such%20as%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt4-ai-model-got-lazier-dumber-chatgpt-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGPT-4%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20computing%20brain%20behind%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20burst%20on%20the%20scene%20in%20late%202022%2C%20parallel%20computing%20already%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20turbocharge%20the%20kind%20of%20data%20science%20that%20serves%20up%20relevant%20internet%20ads%2C%20optimizes%20supply-chain%20decisions%2C%20and%20attempts%20to%20detect%20online%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20Nvidia%20has%20had%20a%20long%20relationship%20with%20Pydata%2C%20a%20conference%20for%20developers%20who%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-python%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPython%20coding%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20do%20data%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Ratzel%20was%20there%20to%20introduce%20a%20new%20software%20tie-up%20with%20Nvidia%20for%20Python%20developers%20using%20common%20open-source%20data%20management%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20with%20a%20data%20set%20of%20movie%20reviews%20and%20numerical%20ratings.%20The%20aim%20was%20to%20make%20good%20recommendations.%20Ratzel%20had%20to%20match%20the%20taste%20of%20movie%20reviewers%20as%20closely%20as%20possible%20with%20a%20person's%20taste.%20The%20math%20to%20determine%20who%20had%20similar%20tastes%20wasn't%20that%20complicated.%20But%20the%20calculations%20involved%20large%20amounts%20of%20data%20on%20330%2C000%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20giant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERunning%20the%20initial%20analysis%20took%20two%20hours%20on%20a%20traditional%20computer%20with%20a%20CPU%2C%20he%20said.%20A%20few%20tweaks%20got%20that%20down%20to%20one%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20Ratzel%20switched%20to%20a%20GPU%20and%20ran%20the%20analysis%20again.%20He%20got%20it%20done%20in%20less%20than%20two%20seconds.%20That%20speed%20comes%20from%20the%20parallel%20computing%20that%20the%20GPU%20enables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20has%20been%20around%20since%20the%201980s%2C%20but%20until%20relatively%20recently%2C%20the%20capability%20to%20actually%20perform%20parallel%20computing%20was%20hard%20to%20access.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erise%20of%20GPU%20availability%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-negotiating-huge-cloud-deal-supply-ibm-with-nvidia-gpus-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud%20providers%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20for%20eager%20data%20scientists%20to%20complete%20their%20own%20projects%20in%20seconds%20rather%20than%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20much%20time%20saved%2C%20researchers%20can%20run%20many%20more%20experiments%20and%20take%20on%20a%20lot%20more%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20how%20this%20changes%20how%20you%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Ratzel%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20I%20can%20try%20lots%20of%20things%2C%20do%20lots%20of%20experimenting%2C%20and%20I'm%20using%20the%20exact%20same%20data%20and%20the%20exact%20same%20code.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20computations%20GPUs%20perform%20to%20enable%20generative%20AI%20are%20much%20more%20complex%20and%20voluminous%20than%20using%20existing%2C%20structured%20data%20to%20recommend%20movies%20based%20on%20common%20characteristics%20and%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20immense%20volume%20of%20computations%20is%20what%20has%20driven%20so%20much%20demand%20for%20Nvidia%20GPUs.%20And%20that%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20made%20Nvidia's%20business%20so%20valuable%20to%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gpus-cpus-parallel-computing-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731661202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67364575192f525898589948%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gpus-cpus-parallel-computing-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parallel%20computing%20is%20the%20fundamental%20concept%20that%2C%20along%20with%20advanced%20semiconductors%2C%20has%20ushered%20in%20the%20generative%20AI%20boom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%20(Emma%20Cosgrove)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gpus-cpus-parallel-computing-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl