id%20that%20the%20education%20body%20is%20considering%20faster%20degree%20completion%20options%20for%20students.%20Speaking%20at%20southern%20zone%20conference%20for%20autonomous%20colleges%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20students%20will%20soon%20be%20allowed%20to%20complete%20a%20three-year-degree%20course%20in%20two-an-a-half%20years%2C%20and%20four-year%20courses%20in%20three.%20The%20one-day%20conference%20was%20organised%20at%20IIT%20Madras%20to%20prepare%20a%20roadmap%20to%20implement%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%20Academicians%20from%20several%20institutions%20took%20part%20on%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20planning%20to%20implement%20this%20from%20the%20next%20academic%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20when%20asked%20about%20UGC's%20faster%20degree%20completion%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20students%20who%20are%20capable%20can%20complete%20the%20degree%20programmes%20in%20a%20shorter%20duration.%20We%20anticipate%20that%20they%20can%20gain%20six%20months%20to%20one%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%2C%20however%2C%20clarified%20that%20students%20who%20wish%20to%20take%20longer%20to%20complete%20their%20studies%20will%20also%20be%20accommodated%2C%20and%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20breaks%20during%20their%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20is%20based%20on%20the%20recommendation%20made%20by%20IIT%20Madras%20Director%20V%20Kamakoti.%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20detailed%20guidelines%20will%20be%20issued%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20NEP%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20transformation%20of%20education%20system%20that%20will%20benefit%20students%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20onus%20lies%20on%20higher%20education%20institutes%20(HEIs)%20to%20make%20education%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccess%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusivity%20in%20higher%20education%20are%20essen