from-haryana-is-worth-rs-23-crore-know-why%2Farticleshow%2F115244397.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Known%20for%20its%20size%2C%20pedigree%2C%20and%20breeding%20potential%2C%20Anmol%20has%20become%20a%20social%20media%20sensation%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnmol's%20luxurious%20lifestyle%20comes%20at%20a%20high%20cost.%20Its%20owner%2C%20Gill%2C%20spends%20around%20Rs%201%2C500%20daily%20on%20the%20buffalo's%20diet%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20mix%20of%20dry%20fruits%20and%20high-calorie%20foods%20to%20maintain%20Anmol's%20health%20and%20strength.%20The%20menu%20has%20250%20grams%20of%20almonds%2C%2030%20bananas%2C%204%20kg%20of%20pomegranates%2C%205%20kg%20of%20milk%20and%2020%20eggs.%20It%20also%20enjoys%20oil%20cake%2C%20green%20fodder%2C%20ghee%2C%20soybeans%20and%20corn.%20This%20specialised%20diet%20ensures%20that%20Anmol%20is%20always%20prepared%20for%20exhibitions%20and%20breeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnmol's%20health%20is%20also%20maintained%20through%20daily%20grooming.%20The%20buffalo%20is%20bathed%20twice%20a%20day.%20A%20special%20mixture%20of%20almond%20and%20mustard%20oil%20keeps%20its%20coat%20glossy%20and%20healthy.%20Despite%20the%20considerable%20expense%2C%20Gill%20is%20dedicated%20to%20providing%20the%20best%20care%20for%20Anmol%2C%20even%20if%20it%20meant%20selling%20the%20buffalo's%20mother%20and%20sister%20in%20the%20past%20to%20cover%20the%20costs.%20Anmol's%20mother%20was%20known%20for%20producing%2025%20litres%20of%20milk%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Anmol's%20impressive%20size%20and%20diet%20play%20a%20big%20part%20in%20its%20value%2C%20it%20is%20the%20buffalo's%20role%20in%20cattle%20breeding%20that%20truly%20drives%20its%20worth.%20Anmol's%20semen%2C%20collected%20twice%20a%20week%2C%20is%20in%20high%20demand%20among%20breeders.%20Each%20extraction%20is%20valued%20at%20Rs%20250%20and%20can%20be%20used%20to%20breed%20hundreds%20of%20cattle.%20The%20steady%20income%20from%20semen%20sales%20generates%20Rs%204-5%20lakh%20monthly%2C%20helping%20Gill%20manage%20the%20significant%20expenses%20of%20maintaining%20the%20buffalo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20several%20lucrative%20offers%20to%20sell%20Anmol%20at%20its%20Rs%2023%20crore%20valuation%2C%20Gill%20sees%20Anmol%20as%20a%20family%20member%20and%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20parting%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731655500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fo07paqto_anmol-buffalo-_625x300_15_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthis-buffalo-worth-rs-23-crore-enjoys-a-royal-diet-and-almond-oil-massages-everyday-7024291%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20buffalo%20in%20Haryana%2C%20valued%20at%20Rs%2023%20crore%2C%20is%20making%20waves%20at%20agricultural%20fairs%20across%20India.%20The%20buffalo%2C%20named%20Anmol%2C%20weighs%201%2C500%20kg%20and%20has%20been%20the%20centre%20of%20attention%20at%20events%20such%20as%20the%20Pushkar%20Mela%20and%20the%20All-India%20Farmers'%20Fair.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthis-buffalo-worth-rs-23-crore-enjoys-a-royal-diet-and-almond-oil-massages-everyday-7024291%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20WFH%20Techie's%20Password%20Error%20Led%20To%20Travel%20Nightmare%20For%207%20Lakh%20Fliers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20technical%20glitch%20caused%20chaos%20for%20seven%20lakh%20air%20travellers%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20during%20a%20bank%20holiday%20weekend%20in%20August%20last%20year.%20The%20issue%20started%20when%20the%20corrupted%20file%20caused%20a%20breakdown%20in%20flight%20processing%20systems.%20This%20led%20to%20widespread%20flight%20cancellations%2C%20leaving%20travellers%20stuck%20at%20airports%20for%20hours%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F11%2F14%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-air-traffic-employees-work-from-home-day-exacerbated-nightmare-delays-for-70k-travelers-report%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3ENY%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20problem%20grew%2C%20as%20some%20engineers%20were%20working%20from%20home%20that%20day%2C%20and%20were%20unable%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20remotely%20on%20time.%20An%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20a%20critical%20delay%20in%20resolving%20the%20issue%20was%20caused%20by%20difficulties%20in%20authenticating%20a%20remote%20engineer's%20password%20credentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20glitch%20began%20early%20on%20August%2028%2C%202023%2C%20and%20grounded%20flights%20nationwide.%20National%20Air%20Traffic%20Services%20(NATS)%20had%20arranged%20for%20a%20Level%202%20engineer%20to%20be%20available%20on%20call%2C%20but%20not%20on-site%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20an%20exceptionally%20busy%20travel%20day.%20A%20Level%201%20engineer%2C%20who%20was%20present%20at%20NATS'%20Swanwick%20facility%20in%20Hampshire%2C%20immediately%20began%20diagnostic%20procedures%20after%20the%20systems%20failed%20at%208%3A32%20AM.%20However%2C%20the%20engineer%20struggled%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20because%20the%20senior%20technical%20support%20engineer%20was%20working%20remotely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remote%20engineer's%20attempts%20to%20log%20in%20and%20fix%20the%20issue%20were%20delayed%20after%20password%20authentication%20issues%20prevented%20timely%20access%20to%20the%20system.%20It%20took%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20for%20the%20engineers%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20but%20they%20still%20couldn't%20resolve%20the%20problem%20right%20away.%20The%20glitch%20wasn't%20fully%20fixed%20until%20four%20hours%20after%20it%20was%20first%20detected%20but%20not%20before%20causing%20disruptions%20to%20flight%20schedules%20that%20stretched%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ripple%20effect%20of%20the%20disruption%20forced%20airlines%20to%20pay%20out%20over%20%24126%20million%20in%20compensat