cks%20at%20the%20bourses%2C%20with%20most%20counters%20losing%20ground%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fhul-asian-paints-consumption-related-stocks-take-a-hit-as-inflation-bites-124111500736_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20needed%20armor%20so%20badly%20that%20its%20biggest%20film%20studio%20donated%2036%20Soviet-era%20tanks%20that%20were%20used%20as%20props%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22T-55%20and%20T-54%20tanks%20are%20seen%20in%20a%20black-and-white%20photo%20taken%20in%20Hungary.%20Mosfilm's%20director%20general%2C%20Karen%20Shakhnazarov%2C%20wears%20sunglasses%20as%20he%20attends%20a%20meeting%20with%20Vladimir%20Putin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6736d734fa0140cdd563a617%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMosfilm's%20director%20general%20said%20the%20movie%20studio%20had%20donated%2036%20tanks%2C%20including%20the%20aging%20T-55%2C%20to%20Russia's%20defense%20ministry.%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%20via%20Getty%20Images%20and%20Jack%20Esten%2FPicture%20Post%2FHulton%20Archive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussia's%20biggest%20film%20studio%20said%20it%20helped%20shore%20up%20the%20Kremlin's%20losses%20in%202023%20with%2036%20aging%20tanks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMosfilm's%20head%20told%20Putin%20that%20it%20donated%2028%20T-55%20tanks%20and%20eight%20PT-76%20tanks%20to%20the%20defense%20ministry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERussian%20troops%20have%20used%20similar%2C%20aging%20tanks%20as%20fire%20support%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Russia%20hunts%20for%20more%20war%20gear%2C%20its%20biggest%20film%20studio%20has%20stepped%20up%20%E2%80%94%20with%20movie%20props.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20general%20of%20Mosfilm%2C%20Karen%20Shakhnazarov%2C%20met%20with%20Russian%20leader%20Vladimir%20Putin%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20discuss%20the%20studio's%20profits%20and%20film%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20spoke%20mainly%20on%20their%20aspirations%20for%20the%20company%2C%20with%20Shakhnazarov%20boasting%20that%20Mosfilm%20was%20on%20par%20in%20scale%20with%20Hollywood%20firms%20like%20Warner%20Bros.%20and%20Universal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20Shakhnazarov%20ended%20the%20conversation%20on%20a%20note%20about%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Shakhnazarov%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fen.kremlin.ru%2Fevents%2Fpresident%2Fnews%2F75562%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20transcript%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20the%20Kremlin.%20%26quot%3BIn%202023%2C%20we%20handed%20over%2028%20T-55%20tanks%2C%20eight%20PT-76%20tanks%2C%20six%20infantry%20fighting%20vehicles%2C%20and%20eight%20trucks%20we%20had%20in%20our%20military%20department%20to%20the%20Armed%20Forces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20they%20needed%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Shakhnazarov%20added%2C%20saying%20Russia's%20defense%20ministry%20took%20the%20vehicles%20into%20its%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMosfilm%20is%20our%20pride%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20responded%2C%20per%20the%20transcript.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mosfilm's%20director%20general%20sits%20at%20a%20table%20with%20Russian%20leader%20Vladimir%20Putin%20to%20discuss%20the%20studio's%20profits.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6736d5bdede4eeae3927c016%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22580%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20head%20of%20Mosfilm%2C%20Shakhnazarov%2C%20met%20with%20Putin%20on%20Wednesday.%3Cp%3EThe%20Kremlin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20immediately%20clear%20whether%20any%20of%20Mosfilm's%20tanks%20saw%20action%20in%20Ukraine%20or%20whether%20they%20were%20even%20in%20the%20right%20condition%20to%20be%20usable%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mosfilm.ru%2Fservices%2Fmilitary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMosfilm's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20the%20studio%20has%20over%20190%20armored%20vehicles%2C%20armored%20personnel%20carriers%2C%20and%20self-propelled%20guns%2C%20though%20it%20described%20them%20as%20being%20%26quot%3Bdisguised%26quot%3B%20as%20equipment%20from%20various%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20equipment%20is%20props%20(stage%20production%20equipment)%2C%20is%20in%20good%20working%20order%2C%20and%20is%20ready%20for%20filming%20several%20movies%20simultaneously%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20website%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20Soviet-era%20tanks%20mentioned%20by%20Shakhnazarov%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-shows-russia-tank-topped-with-ridiculously-tall-cage-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20medium%20tank%20T-55%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20light%20tank%20PT-76%20%E2%80%94%20were%20produced%20in%20the%201940s%20and%201950s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20T-55%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20produced%20tanks%20in%20the%20world%2C%20was%20a%20hallmark%20of%20the%20early%20Cold%20War.%20It's%20so%20old%20that%20it's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ussalabama.com%2Fexplore%2Ftanks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20featured%20in%20museums%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20militaries%20around%20the%20world%20still%20use%20these%20tanks.%20But%20they're%20two%20generations%20behind%20the%20modern%20arms%20being%20used%20today%2C%20and%20have%20been%20largely%20considered%20obsolete%20in%20Russia's%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Shakhnazarov's%20statement%20comes%20as%20Moscow%20has%20struggled%20to%20maintain%20its%20inventory%20of%20armored%20vehicles%20amid%20heavy%20losses%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFigures%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oryxspioenkop.com%2F2022%2F02%2Fattack-on-europe-documenting-equipment.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDutch%20open-source%20tracking%20group%20Oryx%3C%2Fa%3E%20say%20that%20Russia%20has%20lost%2010%2C888%20armored%20vehicles%20since%20the%20war%20began%2C%20including%203%2C558%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoscow%20has%20been%20driving%20up%20production%20to%20fill%20the%20gap%2C%20dumping%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-crisis-ukraine-war-moscow-inflation-sanctions-putin-spending-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord%206%25%20of%20its%20GDP%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20defense%20spending%20on%20guns%2C%20ammunition%2C%20and%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strain%20on%20its%20forces%20began%20showing%20more%20clearly%20in%202023%2C%20as%20open-source%20intelligence%20groups%20noticed%20tanks%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-taken-tanks-from-1940s-out-of-storage-monitoring-group-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1940s%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-taken-tanks-from-1940s-out-of-storage-monitoring-group-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0including%20the%20T-55%20and%20its%20older%20cousin%2C%20the%20T-54%2C%20being%20taken%20out%20of%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20older%20tanks%20likely%20won't%20fare%20well%20against%20modern%20armor%2C%20but%20researchers%20from%20the%20UK-based%20Royal%20United%20Services%20Institute%20said%20Russian%20troops%20have%20been%20deploying%20them%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-old-tanks-front-line-still-pose-threat-rusi-ukraine-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovide%20artillery%20support%20and%20long-range%20firepower.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20Defense%20Ministry%20and%20Mosfilm%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-mosfilm-studio-donated-soviet-tanks-t55-pt76-ukraine-war-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731654484000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6736d734fa0140cdd563a617%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-mosfilm-studio-donated-soviet-tanks-t55-pt76-ukraine-war-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mosfilm's%20director%20general%2C%20Karen%20Shakhnazarov%2C%20said%20the%20studio%20donated%2028%20T-55%20tanks%20and%20eight%20PT-76%20tanks%20to%20the%20defense%20ministry%20in%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-mosfilm-studio-donated-soviet-tanks-t55-pt76-ukraine-war-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kohli%20'absolutely%20fine'%2C%20no%20major%20concern%20with%20Rahul%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731654328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115327018%2Cimgsize-38456.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-australia%2Fvirat-kohli-absolutely-fine-no-major-concern-with-kl-rahul%2Farticleshow%2F115326579.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20Test%20squad%20held%20match%20simulation%20in%20Perth%2C%20with%20Virat%20Kohli%20batting%20without%20any%20discomfort%20following%20a%20precautionary%20scan.%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20however%2C%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20ball%20and%20unable%20to%20continue%20batting%2C%20raising%20minor%20concerns%20ahead%20of%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAHIL%20MALHOTRA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMy%20Mistake%20To%20Put%20Up%20Wife%20Against%20Supriya%20Sule%26quot%3B%3A%20Ajit%20Pawar%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fajit-pawar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAjit%20Pawar%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadmitted%20that%20it%20was%20a%20mistake%20to%20field%20his%20wife%20Sunetra%20Pawar%20against%20his%20cousin%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupriya-sule%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupriya%20Sule%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Ms%20Sule%2C%20daughter%20of%20NCP%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20had%20defeated%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20representing%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20NCP%20faction%2C%20in%20the%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%201.5%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20my%20mistake%20to%20field%20her%20against%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20I%20have%20told%20you%20again%20and%20again.%20It%20is%20over%20now.%20On%20November%2020%20there%20is%20an%20election%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20the%20voters%20will%20decide%20in%20whose%20hands%20Maharashtra%20should%20be%20given%20for%20five%20years.%20We%20are%20paying%20more%20attention%20to%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20said%20that%20his%20primary%20focus%20remains%20on%20campaigning%20in%20the%20constituencies%20allotted%20to%20the%20NCP%20under%20the%20Mahayuti%20(Grand%20Alliance).%20The%2065-year-old%20said%20that%20despite%20occasional%20calls%20from%20alliance%20partners%20like%20the%20BJP%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%20to%20join%20their%20campaigns%2C%20he%20is%20prioritising%20NCP%20seats.%20%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20with%20only%20a%20few%20days%20left%2C%20I%20am%20concentrating%20on%20our%20constituencies%20and%20holding%20public%20rallies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENepotism%20In%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20said%20that%20political%20families%20have%20played%20a%20role%20in%20all%20major%20parties%2C%20from%20Congress%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20(MNS).%20He%20argued%20that%20ultimately%2C%20it%20is%20the%20voters%20who%20decide%20whether%20a%20candidate%20from%20a%20political%20family%20deserves%20their%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-elections-uddhav-thackeray-abandoned-bal-thackerays-ideology-eknath-shinde-to-ndtv-7023544%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories_lastestImg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOn%20Abuse%20Of%20Power%20Charge%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20%26quot%3BHave%20We%20Arrested%20Anyone%26quot%3B%20Counter%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20speaks%20against%20nepotism%2C%20but%20in%20this%20election%2C%20both%20the%20Mahavikas%20Aghadi%20and%20the%20Mahayuti%20alliances%20have%20numerous%20candidates%20from%20political%20families.%20This%20trend%20has%20been%20part%20of%20Indian%20politics%20for%20decades.%20After%20we%20gained%20independence%20in%201947%2C%20the%20families%20who%20initially%20entered%20politics%20continued%20to%20hold%20influence.%20The%20Congress%20party%20dominated%20government%20for%20many%20years%2C%20bringing%20successive%20generations%20into%20its%20ranks%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20across%20all%20parties%20-%20whether%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20BJP%2C%20or%20even%20the%20MNS%20-%20family%20members%20of%20political%20leaders%20are%20running%20for%20office.%20%C2%A0However%2C%20it's%20ultimately%20the%20voters%20who%20decide.%20Regardless%20of%20family%20ties%2C%20voters%20support%20candidates%20they%20believe%