3Cp%3EBut%20young%20officers%20who%20disagreed%20would%20come%20regularly%20to%20the%20shelter%20to%20try%20and%20change%20his%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrincess%20Mikasa%20recalled%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20frightening%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Bheated%20arguments%20and%20tension%2C%20as%20if%20bullets%20were%20about%20to%20fly%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Asahi%20Shimbun%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20lost%20their%20home%2C%20the%20decades%20that%20followed%20were%20far%20from%20luxurious%20for%20the%20princess%2C%20who%20took%20on%20domestic%20duties%20as%20the%20family%20struggled%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20raising%20my%20children%2C%20Japanese%20society%20was%20still%20in%20a%20difficult%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20her%20100th%20birthday%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20Imperial%20Household%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recall%20with%20deep%20gratitude%20how%20many%20people%2C%20including%20my%20husband%2C%20always%20supported%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20princess%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20of%20Princess%20Misaka's%20sons%20passed%20away%20before%20her%2C%20including%20one%20who%20died%20aged%2047%20while%20playing%20squash%20at%20the%20Canadian%20embassy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMale-only%20succession%20rules%20mean%20that%20Japan's%20royal%20women%20cannot%20ascend%20to%20the%20throne%20and%20must%20forgo%20their%20imperial%20status%20if%20they%20marry%20outside%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrincess%20Misaka%20has%20three%20granddaughters%20who%20remain%20princesses%2C%20including%20Akiko%2C%20whose%202015%20book%20was%20a%20hit%20in%20Japan%2C%20describing%20her%20studies%20at%20Oxford%20and%20an%20incident%20in%20which%20her%20diplomatic%20passport%20caused%20suspicion%20at%20an%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20101-year-old's%20passing%20followed%20reports%20since%20early%20November%20that%20her%20condition%20had%20begun%20to%20deteriora