nd%20landed%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20median%20price%20of%20private%20homes%20in%20Singapore%20was%2013.5%20times%20that%20of%20the%20median%20annual%20household%20income%20of%20%2497%2C124%2C%20per%20the%20Home%20Attainability%20Index%20report.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FMSPUS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedian%20price%20of%20US%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Q3%202024%20is%20about%205.4%20times%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.census.gov%2Ftable%2FACSST1Y2023.S1901%3Fq%3Dmedian%2520income%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20median%20household%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%2477%2C719%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20chanced%20upon%20the%20listing%20while%20browsing%20for%20homes%20online%2C%20Ng%2C%2044%2C%20told%20BI.%20The%20large%2C%20rectangular%20floor%20plan%20drew%20them%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20had%20been%20divided%20into%20seven%20different%20rooms%20and%20was%20being%20rented%20out%20to%20foreign%20workers%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20rundown%20%E2%80%94%20it%20looked%20nothing%20like%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collage%20of%20an%20old%20bathroom%20and%20a%20dirty%20bedroom%20in%20the%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6736c2eeede4eeae3927bfa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20house%20had%20previously%20been%20divided%20into%20seven%20rooms.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Amanda%20Misso.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20still%20tenanted%20when%20the%20couple%20showed%20up%20to%20tour%20the%20unit%2C%20Ng%2C%20who%20works%20in%20hospitality%20and%20entertainment%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20came%20in%2C%20the%20agent%20was%20trying%20to%20show%20us%20the%20bedrooms.%20He%20wanted%20to%20knock%20on%20every%20bedroom%20door%20to%20open%20it%2C%20and%20we%20were%20like%2C%20'It's%20OK%2C%20we%20don't%20even%20need%20to%20see%20those%2C'%26quot%3B%20Misso%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20we're%20going%20to%20gut%20everything%20anyway%2C%20we%20just%20needed%20to%20see%20what%20had%20to%20be%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20paid%20almost%201.8%20million%20Singapore%20dollars%2C%20or%20about%20%241.34%20million%2C%20for%20the%20property%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shelf%20dedicated%20to%20vinyl%20records.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f22e37cfb7f307e57439ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20gutted%20the%20interiors%20of%20the%20house.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20work%20required%2C%20the%20renovations%20went%20smoothly.%20In%20addition%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterior-design-trends-that-are-making-your-home-look-dated-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterior%20designer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20couple%20also%20had%20an%20architect%20to%20help%20them%20plan%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20have%20been%20our%20fourth%20place%20together%2C%20and%20we%20kind%20of%20already%20knew%20the%20functionalities%20we%20wanted%20in%20the%20house%2C%20so%20we%20built%20the%20space%20around%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Misso%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20couple%20knew%20they%20wanted%20a%20large%20dining%20and%20kitchen%20area%20where%20they%20could%20have%20an%20island%20counter.%20While%20the%20master%20bedroom%20would%20have%20an%20ensuite%2C%20they%20wanted%20a%20Jack%20and%20Jill%20bathroom%20for%20the%20other%20two%20bedrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f22e37cfb7f307e57439c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20had%20an%20ID%20and%20an%20architect%20to%20help%20them%20design%20their%20space%2C%20including%20the%20bathrooms.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20wanted%20to%20preserve%20some%20of%20the%20house's%20original%20features%2C%20like%20the%20red%20brick%20wall%20that%20runs%20along%20the%20hallway%20and%20into%20the%20courtyard%20in%20the%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20got%20them%20thinking%20about%20using%20other%20pops%20of%20colors%20to%20brighten%20their%20space%2C%20Ng%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20went%20with%20olive%20green%20cabinets%20for%20the%20kitchen%20and%20got%20a%20dining%20table%20in%20a%20matching%20shade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20features%20pops%20of%20color.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f22e41d17aa3c7b2b54e99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThey%20used%20pops%20of%20color%20to%20add%20character%20to%20their%20home%2C%20including%20olive%20cabinets%20in%20the%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EAmanda%20Goh%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20spice%20things%20up%2C%20they%20opted%20for%20an%20icy%20blue%20water%20dispenser%2C%20which%20occupies%20a%20prime%20position%20in%20the%20center%20of%20their%20kitchen%20island.%20An%20orange%20sculptural%20lamp%20hangs%20overhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20previous%20place%20was%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-home-look-mid-century-for-cheap-according-to-designers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emid-century%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20grunge.%20Now%20when%20our%20friends%20come%20by%2C%20they're%20always%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20