%20beacons%20of%20transparency%2C%20to%20end%20the%20chronic%20disease%20epidemic%2C%20and%20to%20Make%20America%20Great%20and%20Healthy%20Again!%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-tracker-robert-f-kennedy-jr-anti-vaccine-activist-named-head-to-us-health-department-7022811%C2%A0%5C%22%3ETrump%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20was%20born%20on%20January%2017%2C%201954%2C%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20He%20is%20the%20third%20of%20eleven%20children%20of%20former%20US%20Attorney%20General%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%20and%20Ethel%20Skakel%20Kennedy%2C%20and%20the%20nephew%20of%20former%20President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy.%20Both%20his%20father%20and%20uncle%20were%20assassinated%20in%20the%201960s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20studied%20at%20Harvard%20University%2C%20attended%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20and%20earned%20a%20law%20degree%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Virginia.%20Later%2C%20he%20completed%20a%20Master's%20Degree%20in%20Environmental%20Law%20from%20Pace%20University%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20where%20he%20co-founded%20the%20Environmental%20Litigation%20Clinic%20and%20served%20on%20the%20faculty%20for%20over%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201980s%2C%20Mr%20Kennedy%20founded%20the%20Waterkeeper%20Alliance%2C%20an%20organisation%20focused%20on%20clean%20water%20advocacy%2C%20where%20he%20worked%20as%20chairman%20and%20attorney.%20His%20work%20to%20restore%20New%20York's%20Hudson%20River%20earned%20him%20the%20title%20%26quot%3BHero%20for%20the%20Planet%26quot%3B%20from%20TIME%20Magazine%20and%20helped%20create%20over%20300%20similar%20Waterkeeper%20groups%20worldwide.%20He%20also%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20New%20York%20City%20watershed%20agreement%2C%20now%20viewed%20as%20a%20global%20example%20of%20sustainable%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kennedy%20founded%20Children's%20Health%20Defense%20to%20address%20their%20health%20issues%20and%20harmful%20exposures%2C%20serving%20as%20chairman%20and%20lead%20counsel.%20While%20claiming%20to%20support%20vaccine%20safety%2C%20he%20has%20also%20been%20found%20spreading%20false%20theories%2C%20such%20as%20vaccines%20causing%20autism%20and%20COVID-19%20being%20targeted%20at%20specific%20ethnic%20groups.%20Before%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20Mr%20Kennedy%20was%20already%20leading%20campaigns%20against%20vaccines%20and%20collaborating%20with%20anti-vaccine%20groups.%20His%20organisation%20has%20also%20filed%20lawsuits%20against%20news%20outlets%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20bias%20against%20anti-vaccine%20views.%20Studies%20show%20his%20Twitter%20account%20was%20a%20major%20source%20of%20vaccine%20misinformation.%20Mr%20Kennedy%20has%20also%20met%20with%20anti-vaccine%20activists%20and%20supported%20anti-vaccine%20literature%2C%20despite%20evidence%20that%20vaccines%20are%20safe%20and%20necessary%20for%20public%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Mr%20Kennedy's%20legal%20wins%20include%20cases%20against%20Monsanto%20in%202018%20and%20DuPont%20in%202019%20for%20contamination%2C%20which%20inspired%20the%20movie%20Dark%20Waters.%20He%20has%20also%20advocated%20for%20Indigenous%20groups%20in%20North%20and%20South%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kennedy%20has%20authored%20several%20books%2C%20including%20bestsellers%20Crimes%20Against%20Nature%20(2005)%20and%20The%20Real%20Anthony%20Fauci%20(2021).%20He%20has%20also%20written%20children's%20books%20on%20American%20history%20and%20Saint%20Francis%20of%20Assisi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%20is%20married%20to%20actress%20Cheryl%20Hines%20and%20has%20seven%20children%20from%20three%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731645240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fd2ml1er_robert-f-kennedy-jr-afp_625x300_15_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F