0is%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%2C%20every%20second%20counts.%20Timely%20treatment%20can%20be%20the%20difference%20between%20life%20and%20loss%2C%20hope%20and%20despair%20for%20the%20entire%20family.%20The%20sooner%20they%20get%20treated%2C%20the%20better%20their%20chances%20of%20survival%20and%20recovery.%20But%20here%20in%20India%2C%20countless%20children%20face%20a%20difficult%20reality%3A%20even%20as%20they%E2%80%99re%20diagnosed%2C%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20get%20the%20specialised%20care%20they%20need%20due%20to%20financial%20barriers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20spread%20awareness%20against%20cancer%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20highlighting%20this%20urgent%20issue%20and%20sharing%20how%20we%20can%20change%20this%20stark%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20day%20one%2C%20our%20mission%20as%20a%20foundation%20has%20been%20to%20ensure%20healthcare%20access%20for%20the%20most%20marginalised%20communities%20in%20the%20country.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20committed%20to%20improving%20healthcare%20for%20children%20through%20initiatives%20like%20the%20%E2%80%98Cochlear%20Implant%20Program%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%20Program%E2%80%99%2C%20now%20integrated%20into%20our%20%E2%80%98Hans%20Pediatric%20Program%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Pediatric%20Program%20aims%20to%20help%20children%20overcome%20disabilities%20and%20serious%20health%20issues%2C%20providing%20support%20for%20congenital%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20hearing%20impairments%20and%20heart%20defects%2C%20as%20well%20as%20care%20for%20epilepsy%2C%20cancer%2C%20NICU%2FPICU%20needs%2C%20and%20bone%20marrow%20transplants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20those%20initiatives%2C%20we%20witnessed%20firsthand%20the%20life-changing%20impact%20that%20prompt%20intervention%20and%20dedicated%20care%20can%20have%20on%20children%20who%20might%20n